# Format: <type>: <short imperative summary>
# Example: docs: add environment validation gates
# Keep summary under 72 characters when practical.
#
# Common types:
# feat     New functionality
# fix      Bug fix
# docs     Documentation-only changes
# refactor Code restructuring without behavior change
# chore    Maintenance, cleanup, tooling
# ci       CI/CD or automation changes
# test     Tests added or updated
# perf     Performance improvement
#
# Why:
# - What problem does this change solve?
# - Why is it worth making now?
#
# What:
# - Main change 1
# - Main change 2
#
# Validation:
# - Command run
# - Manual check performed
#
# Refs:
# - Optional issue, ADR, task, or node id
